<li>Thinking of you and your family during this incredibly challenging time.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you navigate this sorrow.</li>
<li>Words seem inadequate, but please know that I am here for you all.</li>
<li>Please accept my deepest condolences on the passing of your [loved one's name].</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you and your family during this time of grief.</li>
<li>Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>I am deeply sorry for your loss. May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Holding your family close in my heart.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy on the loss of your beloved [loved one's name].</li>
<li>Sending love and support to you all.</li>
<li>May the love you shared bring you solace during this difficult time.</li>
<li>I am thinking of you and your family.</li>
